reviews.reviewText: These are pretty thin - single layer - and colored on only one side. A bit rough in texture. The colors are really appealing and give a more upscale look to a table. They didn't fall apart when I put a wet glass on it. I even sprinkled water on it and it was surprisingly absorbent. I think they'd do well for hors d'oeuvres. I don't know about the absorbent quality with greasy food. Overall, colors are nice and not that bad performance.
